title: Quarto Hello World website
text:
Testing out the quarto-dev/quarto-actions/publish@v2 GitHub Actions workflow to automate website GitHub Pages website publishing.
See the website for this repo at https://jpdunc23.github.io/quarto-hello-world/



Make changes to any file rendered by quarto.
Commit and push.
Wait for the GitHub action to run.
Changes should be reflected on live website.
